      <label>Fig. 1</label>
      <caption>
        <p>Locations of 1765 outpatient health facilities in Kenya from where malaria proportion data were used in this study. Data represented the monthly proportion of outpatient treatments at each facility for malaria and spanning the period January 1996&#x2013;December 2002.</p>
